ates every 8 hours at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using a weighted average of premium and interest components. The exchange applies a ±0.375% funding rate cap to prevent extreme payments during volatile periods. Funding payments are automatically debited or credited to traders' accounts based on their position size and the prevailing rate at settlement time."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
